Islamist Al-Shabaab rebels in Somalia ban mobile phone money transfers, saying they are "unIslamic". (BBC) (AFP)A court in Uganda orders a newspaper to cease publishing the names and photographs of people it says are homosexual, following attacks on homosexuals in the past month. (BBC)David Tamihere is granted parole after serving 20 years imprisonment for the 1989 murders of two Swedish backpackers in New Zealand. (NZ Herald)